MORE SEATS FOR PASSENGERS!
MORE SPACE FOR SHIPPERS!
Now - Most Complete Service Ever Offered on United's Main Line Airway
United's new spring-summer schedules offer more Mainliner service
coast to coast and border to border than at any other time in our quarter-
century history. There are 56 United flights daily from Chicago alone!
New daylight and overnight DC-6 Mainliner 300 flights have been
scheduled to provide additional service for coast-to-coast passengers
and shippers.
At the same time, United has made available more
frequent DC-6 Mainliner 300 nonstops each way between Chicago and
major cities on both coasts.
NOW, MORE THAN EVER, UNITED IS THE FAST, CONVENIENT WAY TO SHIP AND TRAVEL!
